like":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T03:19:03.000Z","msg":"On9?你講完自己唔羞恥？<br />\n做free rider好好玩？"},{"pid":"d43a51a066ff6d86913aef5d4d5c05cdbf64ab4c","tid":1701700,"uid":196087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T03:57:28.000Z","msg":"你係唔係成世唔SL/轉工？<br />\n唔識早少少出門一齊衝？做freerider做到咁無恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"410e5d5d269a28db7ca53075299e4136b625f901","tid":1701700,"uid":278004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T04:01:36.000Z","msg":"講到尾咪又係自撚私<br />\n其實你都出埋去塞<br />\n咪可以制造被罷工囉<br />\n唔係乜都等人哋做"},{"pid":"de6643f71779be1d8dfeddfcf8f9bfa8b7bd9f54","tid":1701700,"uid":35547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T04:24:52.000Z","msg":"乜撚野被罷工就可以成為其中一員<br />\n姐係到時唔能夠被罷工就唔認係同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講到1999其實都係想坐享其成等人幫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母你呢d純粹打工仔心態 <br />\n諗自己利益 唔想返工都要人幫 借個政治事件去幫你<br />\n其實就唔係諗件事本身 而係想借件事令到自己唔洗返工為主姐<br />\n睇死你到時被罷工失敗又發撚曬晦氣咁"},{"pid":"253c41cd279f8134ce3300e29f560e0837f86338","tid":1701700,"uid":313764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T04:26:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3cdzid4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3cdzid4.png&h=568e94ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天氣一凍，好易有貓貓捐入車底取暖架!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1702635\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1702635</a>"},{"pid":"4fd5b8c2bb723fc1ba9d54151a3750afc0f92dd5","tid":1701700,"uid":260680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T04:56:06.000Z","msg":"睇死聽日係遲到既姐,<br />\n結局都係返到工,<br />\n似山竹個次咁"}]}